us/2070757581228773651", "text": "Middle Distillates; Supplies Rise, Prices fall\nGlobal middle distillate seaborne supplies have moved above the seasonal average for June and are expected to rise further as the strait of Hormuz opens up\n#oott https://t.co/6M1QHaRD3V", "time": "06:34", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 7587, "likes": 24, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2070810619604033984", "url": "https://x.com/Energy_Tidbits/status/2070810619604033984", "text": "The Master of Tanker reported being hit by unidentified projectile, looks like just offshore Oman in/near the Strait of Hormuz.\n\n #oott   Thx @UK_MTO", "time": "10:05", "author": "Energy_Tidbits", "author_name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "views": 1355, "likes": 4, "replies": 1, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2070818493029847155", "url": "https://x.com/Energy_Tidbits/status/2070818493029847155", "text": "Bahrain says Iran launched drone attack on its territory.  No reports yet of damage.\n\nTimely story? ICYMI, 👇@WSJ report \"How Iran Devasted an American Naval Base [in Bahrain] - and caused a U.S. Recalculation\"   Thx @anikaaseth @shelbyholliday @deniseduana @milanczerny \n\n#oott", "time": "10:36", "author": "Energy_Tidbits", "author_name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "views": 5700, "likes": 2, "replies": 1, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2070819496424779876", "url": "https://x.com/Energy_Tidbits/status/2070819496424779876", "text": "Reminder Bahrain is less than 100 km from the world's largest oil export terminal, Saudi Aramco Ras Tanura  [also a refinery] , and Qatar's Ras Laffin LNG production and export terminal.  Both of which have been hit by drones since the US attacked Iran. \n\n#oott https://t.co/JUd61e3Htl", "time": "10:40", "author": "Energy_Tidbits", "author_name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "views": 3484, "likes": 10, "replies": 1, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2070828154134966312", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2070828154134966312", "text": "The Omani route in the Strait of Hormuz is now operating in both directions (previously, tankers were encouraged only out, rather than in). Now, the route is cleared also for inbound tankers. https://t.co/T2EBjJhTcF", "time": "11:14", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 133024, "likes": 674, "replies": 95, "retweets": 167, "quotes": 23, "bookmarks": 96, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2070888390992478434", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2070888390992478434", "text": "WTI futures are over-sold\n\nPrice fell $7.37 (10%) from $76.60 to $69.23 week ending June 26\n\n12-month spreads suggest somewhat lower prices on Monday\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/okb0SIvb9U", "time": "15:14", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 4118, "likes": 49, "replies": 2, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2070895836372836698", "url": "https://x.com/NoamRaydan/status/2070895836372836698", "text": "1/4 Iran's actions show that traditional arrangements in Hormuz have collapsed &amp; a new system is taking shape aimed at cementing Iranian control. Unless circumstances change significantly, this shift may not be temporary. My latest:  https://t.co/4A3tOBbuio\n#OOTT #Shipping #Iran", "time": "15:43", "author": "NoamRaydan", "author_name": "Noam Raydan", "followers": 7546, "views": 29255, "likes": 77, "replies": 12, "retweets": 35, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 43, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2070901157363421319", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2070901157363421319", "text": "WTI  12-month spread narrowed $3.93 (57%) for the week ending June 26\n\n6-month spread narrowed $2.43 (59%) \n\nPrice fell $7.37 (10%) from $76.60 to $69\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/cJvBXMieX6", "time": "16:04", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 3060, "likes": 20, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2070905534555812038", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2070905534555812038", "text": "Brent futures 12-month spread narrowed $4.33 (74%)\n\n6-month spread narrowed $2.90 (95%) for the week ending June 26\n\nFront-month price fell $7.86 (10%) from $79.85 to $71.99\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/INVK27tbzr", "time": "16:22", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 3171, "likes": 18, "replies": 4, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": 